{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 863249302, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 55, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 17:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们是不是把川普带入成一个正常的普通人思想了？<br/>正常的一国元首会自己画K线然后叫儿子操作期货挣钱？<br/>把他想象成正常人的你们才是不正常。。。。", "lou": 1760, "content_length": 135, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775122038}, {"pid": 863250099, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 28, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 17:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "就好像现在停在海峡那些油轮为什么不走？他们为什么不换个航道绕远出去？因为都是利益啊<br/>船员得益 船主得益 租船公司得益 大家都受益只要没有生命危险 有钱为什么不挣<br/>利益才是一切的根本。初中政治没教过资本主义的概念吗？不要拿我们这一套去套别的地方  我们是具有特色的", "lou": 1761, "content_length": 246, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775122462}, {"pid": 863253208, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 18:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "做期货的  夜盘期货一定要谨慎一点啊，现在油的预期打得过高了  我夜盘肯定要下杠杆 不然太危险了 <br/>金做到夜盘可以空单止盈了。<br/>期货最有把握的一段也过去了  接下来都是变数", "lou": 1762, "content_length": 152, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775124113}, {"pid": 863254079, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 18:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863253825,45974302,3321]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67128393]屁股决定脑袋xx[/uid] (2026-04-02 18:07):[/b]<br/><br/>黄金可以开空了吗狼大[/quote]<br/>。。。我都准备止盈了 。。。", "lou": 1763, "content_length": 31, "reply_to": 863253825, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775124602}, {"pid": 863263252, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 19:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我不吃最后一点收益了  杠杆多油空金全部止盈  回收现金等下一次确定性机会<br/>目前4层黄金多单无杠杆  3层多油无杠杆 <br/>收手收手", "lou": 1764, "content_length": 108, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775130522}, {"pid": 863264192, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 19:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863263491,45974302,3323]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60147900]gsctsxlz2012[/uid] (2026-04-02 19:51):[/b]<br/><br/>这位置的铁盒不能重，买多了没那么快回去。[/quote]<br/>对的 没有趋势级别行情 那就不用考虑ETF能持续上涨 但是目前做个套利没什么问题 因为没什么手续费。一个点就是一个点的收益", "lou": 1765, "content_length": 116, "reply_to": 863263491, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775131183}, {"pid": 863266184, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 20:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863264286,45974302,3323]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66883984]kkk_facai[/uid] (2026-04-02 20:00):[/b]<br/><br/>原油：航运数据显示，委内瑞拉3月石油日出口量突破100万桶大关，为六个月来首次。委内瑞拉正重新成为国际油市的重要补充来源。<br/><br/>委内瑞拉石油卖了装谁兜里，好难猜啊。[/quote]<br/>所以下午还有人和我说不是卖委内瑞拉的油。。。。我很无语。。。我都不懂那些人的资料哪来的 。。。。想纠错都不懂怎么纠错 因为就没有一句是对的。。。", "lou": 1766, "content_length": 145, "reply_to": 863264286, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775132681}, {"pid": 863268230, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 20:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "放轻松  WTI是因为前两天压太狠了  但布油已经涨不动了  A50也在反弹 美股现在也受早上川普的讲话影响 盘前下跌也在可控幅度内<br/>而且我们还开门 他们是不开门了 相当于今天他们也是出金日。所以目前问题不大", "lou": 1767, "content_length": 180, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775134192}, {"pid": 863269496, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 21:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863269263,45974302,3324]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63411336]人在江湖走啊[/uid] (2026-04-02 21:02):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202604/02/jmQ2x-b0mlZbT3cSry-sg.jpg[/img]<br/>凉凉嘛[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>那条疯狗不会让川普撤那么容易的 不然他就要承受一切反扑", "lou": 1768, "content_length": 57, "reply_to": 863269263, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775135111}, {"pid": 863270285, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 21:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这波真是给大鹅回了一波大血，所以之前俄乌的时候我就说了 其实最痛的还不是大俄 而是欧公子<br/>欧公子买完单后轮到白头巾了 这个也是我这回的判断，白头巾要给的钱比朗子还多", "lou": 1769, "content_length": 156, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775135640}, {"pid": 863271246, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 21:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863271076,45974302,3325]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=10055213]ilovehoneyxue[/uid] (2026-04-02 21:22):[/b]<br/><br/>大鹅回血之后就是干日本和德国了，磨刀霍霍[s::34][/quote]<br/>大鹅主要还是要对付欧工资，小日子自有人来解决他     [del]是谁我不能说 反正总不能说是我们[/del]", "lou": 1770, "content_length": 88, "reply_to": 863271076, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775136299}, {"pid": 863273727, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 4, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 21:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863273104,45974302,3326]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38881553]Peace Maker[/uid] (2026-04-02 21:47):[/b]<br/><br/>油金不会对冲吗，同时开多单？[/quote]<br/><br/>那是我的底仓 长线", "lou": 1771, "content_length": 21, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863273104, "postdatetimestamp": 1775138044}, {"pid": 863274699, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 22:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "明天别搞个高开那就完了 别V那么多啊…", "lou": 1772, "content_length": 35, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1775138667}, {"pid": 863275046, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 22:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863274901,45974302,3327]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66056898]行云式[/uid] (2026-04-02 22:06):[/b]<br/><br/>我又回忆起白上黄下的恐怖故事了，狼大。[/quote]<br/><br/>明天大概率黄上 问题别高开啊…明天不可能持续放量的…时机不允许", "lou": 1773, "content_length": 65, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863274901, "postdatetimestamp": 1775138914}, {"pid": 863275411, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-02 22:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863275275,45974302,3327]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=23841879]dsjohn5302[/uid] (2026-04-02 22:11):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大求解，如果明天来个大高开，要怎么操作，竞价直接跑路吗[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/><br/>这个不存在这种可能", "lou": 1774, "content_length": 23, "from_client": "8 Android", "re